More than One Picture: An Art History of the covidBR

Source: vignettes/art.Rmd
art.Rmd

The COVID-19 pandemic was and continues to be an unprecedented historic event. Here, we present cute and colorful illustrations that present the theme in a playful manner. We hope you enjoy it!

A picture is worth a thousand words!

You are encouraged to use the accompanying artwork when using or teaching covidBR! Please remember to credit if you repost (“Artwork by Ariana Moura Cabral”).
